task.summary: Update the minibatch, but seems the results was not good compared to the former one
Back to no minibatch track and modify the env with a fixed penalty length of drug
Update the penalty term by uniform penalty index for the two drugs if on treatment, then index +1 else index -1. In this way, once on treatment the penalty will go rise with one or two drugs.
